Stuck?
--------
Check the Wiki for help. https://github.com/alanwoolley/CorsixTH-Android/wiki

--------
What's broken?
--------
*	Music
*	CorsixTH doesn't support screen resolutions below 640x480 yet, so some of the UI will be obscured or fall off the display.
